    <title>Test-Blog(Video &amp; Audio)</title>
    <url>/2020/02/24/test-blog/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="测试内容"><a href="#测试内容" class="headerlink" title="测试内容"></a>测试内容</h1><p>该博客文章用于测试视频、音频播放相关的内容</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<p>测试1.<br>    音频播放：<br>    主要采用加载本地音乐的方式，并非音乐网站上歌曲的链接<br>    （由于github服务器在国外，所以延迟很大、加载很慢，建议缓冲后再试听！）</p>

        <div id="aplayer-ffIpINOw" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <pre class="aplayer-lrc-content"></pre>
        </div>
        <script>
          var ap = new APlayer({
            element: document.getElementById("aplayer-ffIpINOw"),
            narrow: false,
            autoplay: false,
            showlrc: false,
            music: {
              title: "LUV(Remix inst.)",
              author: "Apink",
              url: "Apink - LUV(Remix inst.).mp3",
              pic: "",
              lrc: ""
            }
          });
          window.aplayers || (window.aplayers = []);
          window.aplayers.push(ap);
        </script>

<p>测试2.<br>    视频播放：<br>    主要采用加载本地视频的方式，并非视频网站上视频的链接<br>    （由于github服务器在国外，所以延迟很大、加载很慢，建议缓冲后再观看！）<br>            <div style="text-align:center"><br>            <button onclick="playPause()">播放/暂停</button><br>            <button onclick="makeBig()">放大</button><br>            <button onclick="makeSmall()">缩小</button><br>            <button onclick="makeNormal()">普通</button><br>            <br><br>            <video id="video1" width="420"><br>                <source src="周杰伦 - 说好不哭(卡拉OK版).mp4" type="video/mp4"><br>            </video><br>        </div><br>        <script><br>            var myVideo=document.getElementById("video1");<br>            function playPause()<br>            {<br>                if (myVideo.paused)<br>                    myVideo.play();<br>                else<br>                    myVideo.pause();<br>            } </p>
<pre><code>    function makeBig()
    { 
        myVideo.width=560; 
    } 

    function makeSmall()
    { 
        myVideo.width=320; 
    } 

    function makeNormal()
    { 
        myVideo.width=420; 
    } 
&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre>]]></content>
